He's not showing any symptoms.

352
00:16:04,256 --> 00:16:07,991
安全起见 我还是去一趟急诊室吧
I guess I'll just go to the emergency room to be safe.

353
00:16:07,993 --> 00:16:10,193
霍霍 你想太多了
Howie, this is just your hypochondria.

354
00:16:10,195 --> 00:16:12,245
不 当我坐在了静音键上
No, when I sat on the mute button

355
00:16:12,247 --> 00:16:14,614
