and thought I'd gone deaf, that was my hypochondria.

356
00:16:23,458 --> 00:16:26,376
我们换个时间再告诉他我怀孕了吧
We'll find another time to tell him I'm pregnant.

357
00:16:33,118 --> 00:16:35,285
我想表达的是 这是我第一次
I mean, this is the first time

358
00:16:35,287 --> 00:16:37,220
和别人分手啊
I've ever broken up with someone.

359
00:16:37,222 --> 00:16:40,023
我只是... 没有想到会伤得这么深
I just... I didn't realize it was gonna hurt this much.

360
00:16:40,025 --> 00:16:42,025
确实会这样的
It really can.

361
00:16:42,027 --> 00:16:44,110
宝宝受够了
All right.

362
00:16:45,564 --> 00:16:48,481
这个一点都不好玩
Nothing about this is fun.

363
00:16:48,483 --> 00:16:51,284
没人想聊一聊旗帜
No one wants to talk about flags,

364
00:16:51,286 --> 00:16:54,821
人家都已经十分钟没说一个字了
and I haven't spoken in over ten minutes,

365
00:16:54,823 --> 00:16:58,157
所以 享受你们的节目吧
so, enjoy your new show, Internet.

366
00:16:58,159 --> 00:17:02,545
Amy Farrah Flower出品的... 陪伴
Dr. Amy Farrah Flower Present... With.

367
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:07,250
