I'm sorry for bothering you.

368
00:17:07,252 --> 00:17:08,618
我马上就挂
I'll hang up now.

369
00:17:08,620 --> 00:17:10,303
等等 Rajesh
No, hold on, Rajesh.

370
00:17:10,305 --> 00:17:12,138
你就没有点同情心
You know, you're not being very sympathetic.

371
00:17:12,140 --> 00:17:14,224
你也知道分手是很难的
You know firsthand that breakups are hard.

372
00:17:14,226 --> 00:17:16,726
好嘛
Fine.

373
00:17:16,728 --> 00:17:19,345
如果你坚持我参与这个的话
If you insist on making me a part of this,

374
00:17:19,347 --> 00:17:21,731
没错 我确实知道这有多伤人
yes, I acknowledge how painful they can be.

375
00:17:21,733 --> 00:17:26,336
但是 伤痛也是有积极意义的
However, pain has an evolutionary purpose.

376
00:17:26,338 --> 00:17:29,322
它能从环境中为我们提供信息
It provides information from the environment

377
00:17:29,324 --> 00:17:31,841
告诉我们这样的行为是对我们不利的
that, uh, behavior isn't good for us.

378
00:17:31,843 --> 00:17:34,210
就像我爱上那个脱衣舞娘的时候
Like when I fell in love with that stripper

379
00:17:34,212 --> 00:17:36,312
我还给她买了一辆普锐斯
and bought her a Prius.

380
00:17:38,516 --> 00:17:40,717
我听不下去了
I'm just gonna push all the buttons.

381
00:17:42,887 --> 00:17:45,521
Raj 你现在这么煎熬我表示很心疼
Raj, now, I'm sorry you're suffering.

382
00:17:45,523 --> 00:17:48,691
当初Amy和我分开的时候 我也很痛苦
When Amy and I were broken up, I also suffered.

383
00:17:48,693 --> 00:17:51,094
就算这听上去很惊人
And this may sound surprising,

384
00:17:51,096 --> 00:17:53,363
但我还是开心自己度过了这个难关
but I'm grateful for having gone through it.

385
00:17:53,365 --> 00:17:55,381
真的吗?
Really?

386
00:17:55,383 --> 00:17:57,517
是的
Yes.

387
00:17:57,519 --> 00:18:01,771
我相信现在我们情比金坚
I believe our relationship now is stronger than ever.

388
00:18:01,773 --> 00:18:04,390
我也这么觉得
So do I.

389
00:18:04,392 --> 00:18:05,892
当初... 我们分开的时候
When... when we were apart,

390
00:18:05,894 --> 00:18:08,027
我明白你对我来说有多重要
I learned how important you are to me.

391
00:18:08,029 --> 00:18:10,229
我也认识到
And I realize

392
00:18:10,231 --> 00:18:12,815
当两个人相爱的时候 有时他们...
that when two people are in love, sometimes they...

393
00:18:12,817 --> 00:18:14,951
