Happy Valentine's Day!

394
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:21,207
我们年轻又欢乐!
We are young and fun!

395
00:18:26,498 --> 00:18:28,531
我收回之前的说法
I stand corrected.

396
00:18:28,533 --> 00:18:30,917
确实挺有意思的
Fun.

397
00:18:40,053 --> 00:18:43,221
一起庆祝这次直播成功吧
Congratulations on a successful live show.

398
00:18:43,223 --> 00:18:45,790
还有这个有爱的情人节
And a lovely Valentine's Day.

399
00:18:47,944 --> 00:18:52,197
打扫一点都不年轻又欢乐
Cleaning up is not young and fun.

400
00:18:52,199 --> 00:18:54,232
这个可以有 纸屑大战!
It can be. Confetti fight!

401
00:18:59,539 --> 00:19:01,573
不如你歇会儿吧
Maybe you should take a break.

402
00:19:01,575 --> 00:19:02,991
我来收拾就好
I got this.

403
00:19:05,796 --> 00:19:10,915
你知道confetti的单数形式是confetto吗?
Did you know the singular of confetti is "confetto"?

404
00:19:10,917 --> 00:19:14,753
有意思 那什么时候用单数形式呢?
Interesting, and when would you use the singular?

405
00:19:14,755 --> 00:19:15,920
真高兴你问了
I'm glad you asked.

406
00:19:15,922 --> 00:19:18,973
Amy 你鼻子里有一张纸屑
Amy, you have a confetto in your nose.

407
00:19:18,975 --> 00:19:21,976
